{"tid":682112,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人忍住晒成套動漫啲感動位但最後先嚟破防?","createTime":"2018-05-28T14:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T03:56:40.000Z","uid":74380,"like":34,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"f53366fcc8dd1136b1a1e90a636e32aa3918f24c","tid":682112,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:48:54.000Z","msg":"好似我咁,例如加旋成套野都勁多感動位,但一直都冇喊出嚟,即使係馬岡消失或者甘草米消失都冇喊,頂籠都係熱淚盈眶,但到最後清麻呂同加旋道別果度真係頂唔順感動到喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋鋼煉都係,明明成套野無論係熱血位或者感動位都冇喊,但到最後賀恩漢係老婆墳前懺悔再消失真係忍唔住流馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廿幾歲人仲咁易喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有其他唔記得,諗到再講,有冇巴打都好似我咁?"},{"pid":"0f8f8fac206cfee3ca3dccad7cfb3fd1df14a0c6","tid":682112,"uid":179121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:53:43.000Z","msg":"不如睇小說：巫師世界"},{"pid":"11889f50b4e68c8922159ae05fb16004382a4ea9","tid":682112,"uid":91931,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:54:05.000Z","msg":"四月<br />\n最後讀信表白三連發"},{"pid":"d171c77b8a8dbb522e6b38a7aeb08c095257c9d9","tid":682112,"uid":94381,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:54:59.000Z","msg":"數碼暴龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c01f3d754fbfb2bf278c90eeb014987d62fc69d","tid":682112,"uid":18912,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:55:13.000Z","msg":"我睇到卡利奧斯完場喊爆道歉我都忍唔住一齊喊出黎"},{"pid":"7669e5cd14797bb19d2d6287532fbc661a8f0f2b","tid":682112,"uid":129660,"like":2,"dislike":39,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我睇re0 <br />\n見到昂咁痛苦 不停掙扎 都睇到喊"},{"pid":"9b80b43a3836f6477bd9eeaad76a6a89e9b9b8b3","tid":682112,"uid":34293,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score